rComments: This professor is amazing. King, educated and well spoken. I took Psychology of Religion with her and it was a very dense course but she made it interesting every class.  Her tests are hard but open book(or at the very least with a cheat sheet) and she gives you the questions well ahead of time. Take courses with her if you can.

Lynda is a greta prof. Very welcoming and really helpful. Encourages participation but doesn't force it. She incorporates contemporary films into the course, which is great! She really wants students to do well and most of them do! I find this course to be really underrated. Take it if you can!

Religion and sexuality. great course. very easy. At times Lynda can be a little difficult to understand (because she is so smart)but she has no problem clarifying things. She truely wants students to do well in her class. Course material is really interesting, and the class makes use of different types of media which is fun. one of the best courses
